OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774192264
OL,3,CKent police officer killed in line of
OL,4,Cduty during emergency callout
OL,6,FA Kent police officer has died and
OL,7,Fanother remains critically ill in
OL,8,Fhospital after their response vehicle
OL,9,Fwas involved in a collision during an
OL,10,Femergency call out.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the force announced
OL,13,Fthe death 'with deep sadness', of PC
OL,14,FBradley Corke, 27, who was based in
OL,15,FTonbridge and had served with the
OL,16,Fforce since May 2022.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
