PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774192264
OL,3,CKent police officer killed in line of
OL,4,Cduty during emergency callout
OL,6,FThe incident, involving a marked Ford
OL,7,FFocus police car and a VW Scirocco,
OL,8,Fhappened on the westbound A20 London
OL,9,FRoad at the junction with Button
OL,10,FStreet, Farningham at approximately
OL,11,F7.45pm.
OL,13,FA member of the public who was in a
OL,14,Fsecond vehicle continues to be treated
OL,15,Ffor serious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
