OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774192264
OL,3,CKent police officer killed in line of
OL,4,Cduty during emergency callout
OL,6,FA spokesman said: "Bradley selflessly
OL,7,Fgave up his life while trying to save
OL,8,Fthe lives of others who were in
OL,9,Fdanger. His bravery, dedication, and
OL,10,Fpassion for helping others will not be
OL,11,Fforgotten."
OL,13,FThey added: "He spent his police
OL,14,Fservice in the towns of West Kent. The
OL,15,Fforce is supporting his family and
OL,16,Fcolleagues, who are devastated."
OL,18,FNeil Mennie, Chair of Kent Police
OL,19,FFederation, said: "We are all
OL,20,Fabsolutely heartbroken to learn of
OL,21,Fthis news.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774192264
OL,3,CKent police officer killed in line of
OL,4,Cduty during emergency callout
OL,6,F"Bradley was a popular colleague who
OL,7,Fwill be much missed and we will be
OL,8,Fdoing all we can to support his family
OL,9,Fand close colleagues at this time.
OL,11,F"Policing is a family and words cannot
OL,12,Fdescribe the pain we are all feeling
OL,13,Fand how this news will affect us in
OL,14,Fthe days, weeks and months ahead.
OL,16,F"This sad incident serves as a
OL,17,Fhorrific example of the risks police
OL,18,Fofficers face and how police officers
OL,19,Fcan sadly make the ultimate sacrifice
OL,20,Fas they strive to keep the public
OL,21,Fsafe."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
